      <title>A Statistical Analysis of Top Marvel Rivals Players</title>
      <link>https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 13:17:00 +0300</pubDate>
      <guid>https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;A friend and I went through the current (2024-12-12) top 100 players in Marvel&#xA;Rivals, and analysed their statistics of their top 3 heroes. Here are the&#xA;results.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Top Heroes&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/1-top-heroes.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Time Played&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/2-time-played.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Matches Played&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/3-matches-played.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Wins&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/4-wins.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;KOs&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/5-kos.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Assists&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/6-assists.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Best KO Streak&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/7-best-ko-streak.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Total Damage&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/8-total-damage.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Best Damage&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/9-best-damage.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Damage Avg per 10 Mins&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/10-damage-avg-per-10-mins.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Total Healing&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/11-total-healing.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Best Healing&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/12-best-healing.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Healing Avg per 10 Mins&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/13-healing-avg-per-10-mins.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Total Damage Blocked&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/14-total-damage-blocked.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Best Damage Blocked&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/15-best-damage-blocked.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Damage Blocked Avg per 10 Mins&#34; src=&#34;https://xphyro.github.io/articles/2024/12/12/marvel-rivals-analysis/plots/16-damage-blocked-avg-per-10-mins.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
